## Success Criteria

### Must Pass (All Required)

- [ ] FPS ≥ 58 when audio analyzer active (measured via `scripts/check_fps.py`)
- [ ] All unit tests pass (≥80% coverage via `pytest --cov=src/vjlive3/audio`)
- [ ] No memory leaks (run 1-hour stress test, RSS stable ±5MB)
- [ ] Works with at least 3 different audio devices (USB, built-in, virtual)
- [ ] Graceful degradation when audio device unplugged (recovery within 5s)
- [ ] Simulation mode produces deterministic outputs for testing
- [ ] Thread-safe: no race conditions in `get_current_analysis()`
- [ ] SAFETY_RAIL compliance: No blocking calls in main thread

### Should Pass (Best Effort)

- [ ] Beat detection accuracy > 90% on test dataset (kick/snare)
- [ ] BPM estimation within ±5 BPM of ground truth
- [ ] FFT frequency resolution < 10Hz per bin at 44.1kHz
- [ ] Startup time < 2 seconds (cold start)
- [ ] Supports sample rates: 44.1kHz, 48kHz, 96kHz

