## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Audio device latency varies | High | Medium | Use fixed buffer sizes, provide latency tuning |
| Thread safety issues | Medium | High | Use RLock, atomic reads, thorough testing |
| Memory allocation during callback | Medium | High | Pre-allocate buffers, use memory pool |
| Device hot-plugging | Medium | Medium | Watchdog thread, automatic reconnection |
| CPU spikes from FFT | Low | Medium | Frame skipping, adaptive quality |
| Platform differences (Windows/Linux/macOS) | High | Medium | Abstract audio backend, CI on all platforms |

